{"type":"object","description":"\"When trigger X fires, run actions Y\" — the building block of a Workflow.\n\ntriggerConfig is a JSON object whose shape depends on triggerType:\n  task.status_changed   → { toStatusId?: uuid, fromStatusId?: uuid }\n  task.assignee_changed → { newAssigneeId?: uuid }\n  task.created          → (none, fires for every new task in the workspace)\n  etc.\n\nAutomationDispatcher (the doctrine listener) reads triggerConfig to filter\nwhich raw domain events should actually trigger this automation.","properties":{"workflow":{"type":"string","format":"iri-reference","example":"https://example.com/"},"name":{"type":"string"},"triggerType":{"type":"string","enum":["task.created","task.updated","task.status_changed","task.assignee_changed","task.closed","project.status_changed","project.closed"]},"triggerConfig":{"description":"trigger-type-specific filter config","type":"object","additionalProperties":{"type":["string","null"]}},"isEnabled":{"default":true,"type":"boolean"},"position":{"default":0,"type":"integer"},"actions":{"readOnly":true,"type":"array","items":{"type":"string","format":"iri-reference","example":"https://example.com/"}},"id":{"readOnly":true,"type":["string","null"],"format":"uuid"},"createdAt":{"readOnly":true,"type":"string","format":"date-time"},"updatedAt":{"readOnly":true,"type":"string","format":"date-time"},"workspace":{"type":"string","format":"iri-reference","example":"https://example.com/"},"version":{"readOnly":true,"default":1,"type":"integer"},"createdByUser":{"type":["string","null"],"format":"iri-reference","example":"https://example.com/"},"updatedByUser":{"type":["string","null"],"format":"iri-reference","example":"https://example.com/"},"enabled":{"readOnly":true,"type":"boolean"}},"x-readme-ref-name":"Automation.html"}